<dl id="n36200b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n36" href="#n36200b">N36 (VI.B.29)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n36all.htm#n36200b"> 200(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> little pot soon hot</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">It is an old saying that &ldquo;<mark>a little pot is soon hot</mark>&rdquo;, which was the case with William the Testy. Being a little man he was soon in a passion, and once in a passion he soon boiled over. <small> Washington Irving, <a name="WINY" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WINY"><cite title="source">A History of New York, by Diedrich Knickerbocker</cite></a> (ed. unknown) 183</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
